[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/kingdomcomedeliverance/mods/1909][img]https://img.shields.io/badge/Mod-Helmet–Off%20Dialog%20[KCD1]-bf4848?style=flat-square–=nexusmods[/img][/url] [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/kingdomcomedeliverance2/mods/1023][img]https://img.shields.io/badge/Mod-Helmet–Off%20Dialog%20[KCD2]-bf4848?style=flat-square–=nexusmods[/img][/url] [url=https://github.com/rdok/kcd2_helmet_off_dialog][img]https://img.shields.io/badge/Open-Source-2ea44f?style=flat-square&logo=github[/img][/url]

This mod automatically takes off your helmet, head chainmail (KCD 1) and coif when starting a conversation with an NPC, then puts them back on when the dialog ends.

